The Advisory Committee shall consist of:
At least the following representatives appointed biennially from a list of eligibles submitted by the Medical and Chirurgical Faculty of Maryland:
1 member of the American Academy of Family Practitioners;
1 member of the American Academy of Pediatricians;
1 member of the American Society of Internal Medicine;
1 member of the American Society of Clinical Pathologists; and
1 member of the American College of Pathology; and
1 representative of the Health Industry Manufacturers Association.
